reviewText: I bought most of these individually as they came out years ago for our grand children. Then when they got older we gave them away. Now that I have a great-grandson I am buying this complete set for him. Our children spent many hours watching these over and over again. They bring a lot of joy.
summary: Great for kids and grownups too.

reviewText: With the complete collection I did not have to keep looking for individual movies. This is a great collection for families, and the children won't be watching the same movie over and over.

reviewText: This collection is a great series for children of all ages.  Glad I purchases it.  My grandchildren and I really enjoy watching it.
Title: Land Before Time: The Complete Collection

reviewText: I've only seen 4 or 5 of these movies, but I liked each one when I was a kid. I'm sure the whole series is great. There are lot's of fun, catchy songs and good messages in the movie. The dinosaur children come across problems that dinosaurs would have, like: sharp teeth (carnivores), asteroids, earthquakes, volcanoes, ect... These movies are full of adventure and fun for kids.
Title: Land Before Time: The Complete Collection

reviewText: I'm so glad I can finally have all the collection of "The Land Before Time" Series with a good price. Thank You Amazon!!!
Title: Land Before Time: The Complete Collection

reviewText: I bought this set as an Easter gift for my 3 and 4 year old nephews and THEY ABSOLUTELY LOVE THESE MOVIES!  I was happy to find the whole set at a great discount!!  The movies were packaged securely and arrived promptly.  I would HIGHLY RECOMMEND!!!  Not only are these movies entertaining, they also teach the little ones life lessons.  Very satisfied with this purchase!!!!
Title: Land Before Time: The Complete Collection

reviewText: I don't have kids/grandkids -- these were for ME!  I had seen one on TV and decided with this price, I couldn't go wrong, and I didn't!No errors were noted in any of the movies and the ability to fast forward or skip the previews was nice.I noted one review complaining that the disks were made in Mexico.  I don't see the prolem -- most disks are now.  The movies themselves were done in England so what's the big deal?Just enjoy Littlefoot, Cera, Spike, Ducky, and Petrie.  It's just a nice "feel-good" set of short movies.
Title: Land Before Time: The Complete Collection

reviewText: We've made it through the first eight of the series now. They are good quality. I have no complaints at all. They were packaged well and shipped and received promptly. Great movies for little kids and kids at heart. They tell a tale that is relevant to geologic history which makes them very educational. Since they are told from the viewpoint of the immature dinosaurs, children find it more relevant to them. Great movies at a super great price.
summary: Great quality a a great deal
Title: Land Before Time: The Complete Collection

reviewText: I have not watched any of the ones out of this collection as I bought it for my newest grandson who's only 4 mths old.  My grandson Jason now watched the series as I purchased but it was passed on to another set of little boys so I jumped at the chance to get the whole collection at one buy instead of individual dvd's like the first time.  Thank you for offering this collection which I think there's one I missed and can't wait to see it.
Title: Land Before Time: The Complete Collection
